===Etymology===
Short for {{m|en|robin redbreast}}. Also from {{der|en|enm|robynet}}, {{m|enm|robynett|t=robin (bird)}}, from the Middle English name {{m|enm|Robynett}}, a diminutive of the Middle English name {{m|enm|Robyn|t=Robin}}.

