===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Any of various [[passerine]] [[bird]]s (about 100 species) of the families [[Muscicapidae]], [[Turdidae]] and [[Petroicidae]] (formerly {{taxlink|Eopsaltriidae|family|ver=161027}}), typically with a red breast.
## A [[European robin]], ''[[Erithacus rubecula]]''.
